sub_title: MSc Marketing management graduate from University of Groningen
summary: An ambitious and result-driven marketing enthusiast with a Master's degree in Marketing from the University of Groningen, I possess an excellent academic record and a steadfast commitment to building a successful career in Marketing and Business Administration. Specialised in areas such as branding, market research, consumer behavior, digital/social media marketing, strategic planning, retail and multichannel marketing, I offer a diverse perspective to drive innovative marketing strategies. My international background provides me with an international way of thinking and abilities to speak multiple languages. I thrive in new situations, always open to learning, and eager to contribute my skills and knowledge to overcome the challenges presented.
